I also I do get the message of searching for license key each time I open the app. Thanks
replyContent: Streaming media over Bluetooth mono may not work in all cars.  The car may not allow it.  For the license, try going into settings, Manager apps, find SoundAbout, clear cache, clear data, force stop (SoundAbout Pro too).  Maybe un-install and re-install.  Make sure you have internet connection after re-install and running the first time.

replyContent: SoundAbout doesn't do anything with the quality of the sound.  If you are trying to send music over Bluetooth mono, then the quality will always be horrible as Bluetooth mono is meant for voice quality sound.  Post what you are trying to do with SoundAbout at http://soundabout.userboard.net and we can figure out what settings will work for you.
